# MokyaLora — License Overview

This repository contains multiple components under different licenses.
Each component's license file is authoritative for its directory.

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 Component                    Directory            License
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 Hardware design files        hardware/            CERN-OHL-S-2.0
 Documentation                docs/                CC-BY-SA-4.0
 Core 0 firmware (Modem)      firmware/core0/      GPL-3.0
 Core 1 firmware (UI/App)     firmware/core1/      Apache-2.0
 MokyaInput Engine (IME)      firmware/mie/        MIT
 IPC protocol definition      firmware/shared/ipc/ MIT
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Full license texts:

  CERN-OHL-S-2.0  →  LICENSE-CERN-OHL-S-2.0.txt
  CC-BY-SA-4.0    →  LICENSE-CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt
